properties.headline: High Wind Warning issued February 6 at 3:34AM HST until February 9 at 11:00AM HST by NWS Honolulu HI
properties.description:
...HIGH WIND WARNING IN EFFECT THROUGH SUNDAY MORNING FOR THE BIG
ISLAND SUMMITS...

* WHAT...Southwest to west winds will increase through the morning
hours over the Big Island summits. Sustained wind speed will
range from 45 to 75 mph with localized gusts over 90 mph.

* WHERE...Big Island Summits.

* WHEN...From 6 AM this morning to 11 AM HST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Travel to the summits is not recommended until winds
have subsided.
properties.instruction:
Take necessary precautions to protect property. Travel to the
summit areas should be delayed until winds subside.

NWSheadline: HIGH WIND WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 6 AM THIS MORNING TO 11 AM HST SUNDAY
